React and Socket.io based Chat Application.
Desktop application.
Not 100% responsive on mobile devices.

Steps to run the Application
-----------------------------
1. Go to client folder
2. Inside Client folder go to Components/Chat
    cd /src/Components/Chat/Chat.js
3. Change ENDPOINT variable 
    const ENDPOINT = 'localhost:5000';  (if required)
4. open new terminal
5. Go to server folder
6. Run Server
    npm start
7. Go to client folder
8. Run Client
    npm start
9. Vist localhost 5000 on browser to see the Application.
